Paper: hep-th/9906186

Date: 1999-06-24

Title: Geometric quantisation of the global Liouville mechanics

Authors: Z. Bajnok, D. Nogradi, D. Varga, F. Wagner

Comments: 5 pages, LaTeX

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A32 (1999) 7477-7481

The reduced SL(2,R) WZW quantum mechanics is analysed in the framework ofgeometric quantization. The spectrum of the Hamiltonian is determined, and itis found, that contrary to the previous approaches, there is a unique,physically preferred quantisation of the system.